features: PREMIUM QUALITY - stationery is made of 70lb premium offset opaque in an uncoated finish and has 96 brightness rating; its distinctive texture and appearance perfectly fit to any personalized writing technique for personal and business correspondence

DIMENSIONS - each paper has a measurement of 8.5 inches x 11 inches; it has a perfect paper size for your heartfelt personalized handwritten and printable messages or calligraphy; it ensures great appreciation of your recipient for its personal touch

DESIGN - its color scheme sets a warm and affectionate mood that features lovely small-petal flowers of Forget-me-Not which symbolizes true and undying love, remembrance, fidelity, and loyalty; this pretty stationery will surely skip your heart a beat

PERFECT FOR ANY OCCASION - our elegant and beautiful stationery paper is perfect for notecards, love letters and poetry, announcements, invitations for Mother's Day, Valentines, Weddings, Anniversary, Graduation, Baby's and all meaningful life celebrations

SECURED AND SAFE PACKAGE - our 100 sheets of beautiful stationery papers are boxed securely in a sturdy box for guaranteed delivery; these are packed to assure that your noteworthy moments with these stationeries are received perfectly and worry-free
body.description: The art of writing a personal note, card, or letter by hand may seem to be a lost art, but the experts agree that such is far from reality. Whether you are a kid, a teenager, or even an adult, our beautiful and stylish stationery set will surely make your heart skip a beat! These will come in handy when making love letter, note cards, announcements, invitation or even a simple caring message on Mother's Day, Christmas, Weddings, Anniversary, Graduation or whatever the occasion, no matter the connection, it will be a terrific way to communicate meaningful thoughts and showcase individual personality.Comes in 6 different elegant floral designs that have been quality crafted and will help you express custom messages in a more traditional way. Every pack comes with 100 pieces of 8.5 in x 11 in stationeries. Compatible with any kinds of ink so you can express yourself through your own handwriting style. Inkjet and Laser Printer-friendly giving you more vibrant results.Many would say why wait for it to travel through the mail when we can contact someone across the globe within minutes? Formality is one of the main reasons handwritten items are still very important. Yes, sending invitations through text is perfectly fine but those regular events that you host every year certainly need a mail delivered invitation.The modern world might have got several communication mediums such as SMS, email, chat etc. However, the practice of using stationery paper has never stopped and people still love it. The first and foremost reason for using stationery is the simplicity in expressing the feelings. Send one now! And make a point of telling the people who mean something to you that you appreciate them.
